  <section class="section"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>LG wall oven — mass-market practical premium</h2>
    <p>LG Electronics' mass-market wall oven tier positions at practical premium — feature-rich at $1.2-3k price point, with LG's signature EasyClean steam-clean cycle + ProBake convection + SmartThinQ Wi-Fi as the technology differentiators against Samsung + GE Profile + Whirlpool mass-market wall ovens. This is distinct from Signature Kitchen Suite, LG's dedicated luxury sub-brand launched 2016 that competes with Wolf + Thermador + Miele at the $4-12k tier. Most LA LG wall oven service calls run at mass-market parts economics — common service parts 2-4 day lead through LG's North American distribution network, control boards and specialty electronics 3-7 days.</p>
  </div></section>

