    <h2>LG wall oven models we service</h2>
    <div class="model-grid">
      <div class="model-card"><h3>LG 30" single built-in wall oven</h3><p>Mass-market single-cavity. EasyClean + ProBake + SmartThinQ. Service: bake element, convection fan + element, control board, sensors, door hardware.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>LG 30" double built-in wall oven</h3><p>Stacked dual-cavity. Upper + lower independent elements + sensors, shared primary control. Per-cavity service patterns.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>LG Wall Oven/Microwave Combination</h3><p>Single 30" cabinet cutout with upper microwave + lower wall oven integrated. Service spans both mechanical systems + shared control panel.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>EasyClean steam-clean system</h3><p>Water-injection + steam-loosen cycle. LA hard-water periodic service on water line + steam nozzles keeps the system spec'd.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>ProBake convection</h3><p>LG's convection implementation — dedicated convection element + fan for multi-rack even cooking.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Self-clean pyrolytic cycle</h3><p>Many LG wall ovens include both EasyClean (routine maintenance) + pyrolytic self-clean (deep cleaning). Pyrolytic service: door-lock motor, thermal sensor, cycle firmware.</p></div>
