    <p><b>F-codes</b> — LG's error code system. F-1/F-3 sensor faults, F-5 door-lock during self-clean, F-7/F-9 control board communication, F-10 door open, F-11 keypad short. Most resolve at sensor or switch level ($200-$400).</p>
    <p><b>EasyClean water-line issues</b> — LA hard water deposits scale on the water-injection system; periodic clearing keeps EasyClean spec'd. Service $220-$360.</p>
    <p><b>ProBake convection element failure</b> — $280-$460.</p>
    <p><b>Bake element failure</b> — 8-12 year typical. $240-$420.</p>
    <p><b>Convection fan motor wear</b> — $320-$520.</p>
    <p><b>Control board lockout</b> — reset resolves some; replacement $420-$720.</p>
